user enters credentials and click on login button
Click on EDGE Device module from side menu bar
Click on EDGE ID search icon i.e. three dots & enter Valid inputs into search text field
After landing on EDGE Device List screen scroll horizontal and Click on EDIT icon button
Click on Well mapping tab module
Click on the three dots of RTUAddress

elements.name: TC080_To verify that a newly created well appears in the Well Mapping list and the user is able to map it to the Edge Device

steps.name: User launch application in chrome browser
user enters credentials and click on login button
Click on EDGE Device module from side menu bar
Click on Setting tab from left side bar and click on well tab from Navigation menu
Click on Add button to add new well
Enter the details for Well Name , Port Number , IP Address and choose the Device Type
Click on Save button To Save Well
Click on EDGE Device module from side menu bar
Click on EDGE ID search icon i.e. three dots & enter Valid inputs into search text field to check well
After landing on EDGE Device List screen scroll horizontal and Click on EDIT icon button
Click on Well mapping tab module
Click on the three dots of well and search for Well Name
Enter the value for Well name to map setting from well module
